comments: Harris (PHI) establishes himself in Kennard's (MEM) path with his arm slightly extended as marginal contact occurs when Kennard moves around the screen.
Kennard (MEM) legally contests Payne's (PHI) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Martin (PHI) briefly grasps Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) jersey and does not pull it away from his body as he absorbs the marginal contact during the post-up.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) brings his off-arm toward Martin's (PHI) side and arm as marginal contact occurs when Jackson Jr. attempts to dribble around Martin in the post.
Martin (PHI) is not vertical when he initiates contact with Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) arm, which affects Jackson Jr.'s post-shot attempt.
Williams Jr. (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it from Oubre Jr. (PHI) after his gather on the driving shot attempt.
Bamba (PHI) briefly grasps and releases Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) jersey before he moves his arms toward a vertical position at the end of Jackson Jr.'s drive.
Bamba (PHI) brings his arms toward a vertical position and absorbs the contact from Jackson Jr. (MEM) during the play at the basket.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) and Bamba (PHI) mutually engage and disengage with one another as marginal contact occurs off-ball.
LaRavia (MEM) moves laterally into Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) path and initiates body contact that affects Oubre Jr.'s SQBR during the drive.
LaRavia (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball and temporarily dislodges it away from Hield (PHI).
Jackson Jr. (MEM) establishes his left foot as his pivot and switches his pivot foot to his right foot when he pivots away from Batum (PHI).
Batum (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball on his initial steal attempt before Jackson Jr. (MEM) briefly grasps Batum's arm, and marginal contact occurs before they disengage on the perimeter.
Batum (PHI) legally contests Aldama's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Aldama (MEM) legally contests Hield's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Hield (PHI) and LaRavia (MEM) engage and disengage with one another as marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Payne (PHI) moves into and initiates body contact that affects Kennard's (MEM) SQBR on his way up the court.

Replay review of the foul called on Aldama (MEM) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Aldama legally contests and cleanly blocks Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) shot attempt at the basket. Due to imminent possession and resumption of play rules, possession is correctly awarded to the Grizzlies.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) initiates illegal contact with LaRavia's (MEM) arm.
Kennard (MEM) legally contests Hield's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Batum (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Williams Jr. (MEM) in the backcourt.
Williams Jr. (MEM) legally contests Batum's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
